name: Way to the end
description:
This game is an open world car adventure game.

Where your goal is to collect maximum number of orbs in the given time and reach the finish point. You can compete with your friends, share your score on  twitter

The game will be hosting an open for all tournament from 25th august, the tournament duration will be 1 month.

Top players at the end of the tournament will be given prize which will depend upon number of downloads.

on 1k downloads- $100

on 10k downloads- top 3 player get $1000

more details about the tournament will be made available on developers twitter profile- Vansh83867477
